abstract: >
  Open-source infrastructure and reference implementation for Argentine
  AI corporations (sociedades de inteligencia artificial) under the
  regime announced by the Ministry of Desregulación on 28 April 2026.
  The package comprises 17 Vercel AI SDK 6 compatible npm libraries
  spanning Mercado Pago, AFIP/ARCA identity + electronic invoicing,
  WhatsApp Business, banking, shipping, GDE/TAD, BCRA, IGJ, Boletín
  Oficial, and Mercado Libre integration; cookbook recipes; five RFCs
  (RFC-001..005) with Zenodo DOIs covering identity, agent discovery,
  cross-jurisdictional audit-log reciprocity, the operational-log wire
  format, and the Ed25519 asymmetric upgrade path; conformance test
  vectors; a public certifier that scores any URL 0-100 against
  RFC-002 + RFC-004 in seconds; a reference implementation that
  self-certifies at 100/100.
